{"tid":461451,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"日本25歲女星自曝「現在還是會和爸爸一起洗澡」，網友崩潰喊噁","createTime":"2017-11-07T14:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T21:09:26.000Z","uid":70917,"like":12,"dislike":78,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"ee83c4eafe627651573b849523a876a19039c990","tid":461451,"uid":70917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:50:01.000Z","msg":"大家小時候應該都會爸媽一起洗澡吧！但是通常長大一點就會開始抗拒這件事情。不過近日在日本一名25歲的女藝人剛力彩芽，她在節目《スッキリ》上表示，他們家到現在都還是有全家人一起洗澡的習慣，讓大家覺得非常驚訝。  <br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/224051_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F224051_fac4ef5554f69012fe38d2f1d4e245a6.jpg&h=e0ceb9cd&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/224133_07aeda4ea7edd4040b997c2716d0431f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F224133_07aeda4ea7edd4040b997c2716d0431f.jpg&h=f87fdc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n剛力彩芽說應該會很多人都認為這樣很奇怪，明明都長大了還和爸媽共浴，但對她來說這是家族共同習慣，他們不會有過多的聯想，也不會覺得不妥。只是沒想到觀眾看完後卻引起一陣反彈，紛紛表示惡心了吧！有的說我尊重你們家的觀念，但無法理解。另外也有網友提出質疑，為什麼她的父母不會覺得這樣不妥，也沒有拒絕女兒一起共浴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/07/224144_b0e2ce051ff9daa7577bcf0e0af46460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F07%2F224144_b0e2ce051ff9daa7577bcf0e0af46460.jpg&h=230fe4ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SgG5JlUA48E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSgG5JlUA48E&d=iBKIxFMy%2FihgnHOHPOon4v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=1983eff3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SgG5JlUA48E</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.teepr.com/827329/jillhsiao/剛力彩芽和父母洗澡/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2F827329%2Fjillhsiao%2F%E5%89%9B%E5%8A%9B%E5%BD%A9%E8%8A%BD%E5%92%8C%E7%88%B6%E6%AF%8D%E6%B4%97%E6%BE%A1%2F&d=iBKIxFMy%2FihgnHOHPOon4v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=2a80144a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.teepr.com/827329/jillhsiao/剛力彩芽和父母洗澡/</a><br />\n<br />\n我都想一齊沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗚呀"},{"pid":"06b62293b514d45e03e46c6d6040ae0f1586a548","tid":461451,"uid":86587,"like":102,"dislike":7,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:57:12.000Z","msg":"狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"074a7afde580c2f67c3357adbd253beaa7535de6","tid":461451,"uid":126648,"like":28,"dislike":2,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"又做新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99e281adc7492324302199511929980257a7901","tid":461451,"uid":60506,"like":6,"dislike":65,"score":-59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"自己個女正常唔會有反應既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26af6d6013374c759976d84fc2373e91de20dd45","tid":461451,"uid":4574,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:01:35.000Z","msg":"純粹係條女乞人憎<br />\n拍戲差 仲成日有得做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b837a9ed2c475bc2415632b8eeb44ab61e81b4b0","tid":461451,"uid":94828,"like":87,"dislike":4,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"個樣成個弱智咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7946e708c15973c617db07870e7129baa1d267","tid":461451,"uid":46155,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T15:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純粹係條女乞人憎<br />\n拍戲差 仲成日有得做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔明點解咁樣衰都上到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40146cde8a59a4b2d35937464fff8950